content: So here is the problem i am high skilled developer ,i was lead dev for 3 year on a  project,but since 2020 nobody is hiring in this area ...They all say that they need developers but does not makes sense why no jobs available ,i applied  for 1000 companies on linked in and others ,but no one is hiring ,,,they ask for your cv and thats it ...I am in Europe ...maybe indians,chinise unfair competition ,i actually don't know and can't understand why the market is down.
